data.description: Welcome home to 6006 Bristol Spur Lane! This stunning 2,533 sq ft 2-story home boasts 4 bedrooms, 3 1/2 bathrooms, and features a ton of beautiful upgrades, not to mention the HUGE upstairs GAMEROOM and the first-floor home office! This amazing home includes an open layout between the living room, kitchen and dining area. Has an unbelievable staircase and showcases tall ceilings and fans. Above all this home is equipped with solar panels for energy efficiency and includes a massive backyard with tons of green space. Is located in the master-planned community of Elyson, featuring a neighborhood swimming pool, splash pad, parks, trails, tennis courts, fitness center, the Elyson Cafe, event space, soccer field, and much more all zoned to Katy ISD! With an amazing location featuring easy access to 99 and I-10, and nearby shopping (Katy Mills and Houston Premium Outlets) and restaurants, this wonderful home has everything! Schedule your visit today!
